Interface CachingBocasService

All Superinterfaces:
BocasService
public interface CachingBocasService
extends BocasService

Interface for a caching bocas repository. Even though the statistics are based on Guava's CacheStats objects implementations are not required to use Guava's caches.

Andres Rodriguez.
